          "instruction": "Apply aᵐ × aⁿ = aᵐ⁺ⁿ",
          "working": "3⁵ × 3⁻³ = 3⁵⁺⁽⁻³⁾ = 3²",
          "result": "3² = 9",
          "voice_text": "When multiplying same bases, add the exponents. 5 plus negative 3 equals 2. 3 squared is 9."
